{"id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MzI4Nw_0004","text":"但我卻衰得感覺享受","structure":{"line_index":4,"char_count":9},"semantics":{"themes":["矛盾情感","沉淪"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["享受","衰"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,5,4,3,3,9,4,9,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["daan6","ngo5","koek3","seoi1","dak1","gam2","gok3","hoeng2","sau6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"但","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"卻","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"衰得","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"感覺","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"享受","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"表達一種矛盾的心理，即使處於不利的境況（衰），卻能從中獲得享受。"},"source":{"title":"Contagious","artists":["薛凱琪"],"lyricists":["林寶"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_3287","prev_line_id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MzI4Nw_0003","next_line_id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MzI4Nw_0005","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
