{"id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MzI4Nw_0006","text":"(看上你每格 夠嗎夠嗎夠嗎)","structure":{"line_index":6,"char_count":13},"semantics":{"themes":["渴望","確認"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["看上","夠嗎"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,5,4,4,3,4,3,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["nei5","mui5","gaak3","gau3","maa1","gau3","maa1","gau3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"(","pos":"PUNCT"},{"text":"看上","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"每格","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"夠","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"嗎","pos":"PART"},{"text":"夠","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"嗎","pos":"PART"},{"text":"夠","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"嗎","pos":"PART"},{"text":")","pos":"PUNCT"}],"syntax_notes":"括號內的副歌部分，重複的問句表達強烈的渴望和對對方關注的確認。"},"source":{"title":"Contagious","artists":["薛凱琪"],"lyricists":["林寶"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_3287","prev_line_id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MzI4Nw_0005","next_line_id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MzI4Nw_0007","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MzI4Nw_0007","text":"逃生口這麼的遠 香薰也沒療效","structure":{"line_index":7,"char_count":13},"semantics":{"themes":["無助","失控"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["逃生口","療效"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,3,9,5,3,3,5,3,3,5,2,0,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["tou4","sang1","hau2","ze5","mo1","dik1","jyun5","hoeng1","fan1","jaa5","mut6","liu4","haau6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"逃生","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"口","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"這麼","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"遠","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"香薰","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"也","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"沒","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"療效","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"描寫一種無助感，即使有逃離的機會，也無法擺脫當下的狀態，連舒緩的方法也失效。"},"source":{"title":"Contagious","artists":["薛凱琪"],"lyricists":["林寶"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_3287","prev_line_id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MzI4Nw_0006","next_line_id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MzI4Nw_0008","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MzI4Nw_0008","text":"(你卻已霎眼) 相當近吧","structure":{"line_index":8,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["距離感","親近"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["霎眼","近"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[4,5,4,2,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["koek3","ji5","saap3","gan6","baa6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"(","pos":"PUNCT"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"卻","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"已","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"霎眼","pos":"VERB"},{"text":")","pos":"PUNCT"},{"text":"相當","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"近","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"吧","pos":"PART"}],"syntax_notes":"括號內的插句，與上一句的「遠」形成對比，強調對方出現的迅速和距離的拉近。"},"source":{"title":"Contagious","artists":["薛凱琪"],"lyricists":["林寶"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_3287","prev_line_id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MzI4Nw_0007","next_line_id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MzI4Nw_0009","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
